= Limitations and alternatives

Despite our best efforts to ensure accessibility of
web.youwen.dev , there may be some limitations. Below is a description of known limitations, and potential solutions. Please contact us if you observe an issue not listed below.

Known limitations for web.youwen.dev
- *Math objects*: Mathematical equations may not be able to be interpreted by
  screenreaders. because Mathematical equations are rendered as raw SVGs,
  with no additional plaintext. Trying to figure out a way to include the
  original plaintext math source code in an ARIA label. Try using a visual
  screen reader.

